<TEXT>
   A poster picturing all 204 men and women who
have flown in space is being carried to the Soviet Union for next
week's summit meeting at which joint superpower space ventures are
to be discussed.
   The framed poster, which symbolizes international cooperation,
was presented by the Smithsonian Institution on Tuesday to Dr.
