   JAMES V. HANSEN
   Income: $110,484-$121,483.
   Honoraria: $18,000.
   Gifts: None.
   Assets: $100,005-$270,000.
   Liabilities: $30,002-$100,000.
   Hansen is a member of the Armed Services Committee, and most of
his honoraria came from speeches to various defense contractors.
</TEXT>
