   ROBIN TALLON
   Income: $155,289-$240,784.
   Honoraria: $13,500, None.
   Gifts: None.
   Assets: $715,003 and up-$1.05 million and up.
   Liabilities: $235,004-$605,000.
   Tallon heavily invests and trades in stocks and properties. He
has received numerous trips in conjunction with speaking
engagements and even gave a speech at the Leonard, Call Taylor
Congressional Classic Tennis tournament in which he participated.
