<1ST_LINE>u w BC-HouseDisclosures-Tennessee     05-25 0434</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>BC-House Disclosures-Tennessee,400</2ND_LINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Here are capsule summaries of the financial
disclosure forms filed by members of the House from Tennessee for
1987 and released Wednesday.
   Income includes the House salary, honoraria earnings from
writing and speeches and other income such as dividends and
