Tammy, and ``I think we're going to see a miracle in the lives of
two people I once despised. I want to see them restored. I love
them.''
   Both Bakker and Swaggart were ousted from their TV operations
after sex episodes, but Swaggart defied his denomination's orders
to stay off the air for a year.
