   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials dropped 1.16 to 1,961.37.
   Gainers outpaced losers by about 7 to 6 on the New York Stock
Exchange, with 784 issues higher, 636 lower and 523 unchanged.
   Big Board volume totaled 138.31 million shares, against 139.93
million in the previous session.
   The NYSE's composite index rose 0.24 to 143.77.
   At the American Stock Exchange, the market value index was up
0.06 at 290.58.
